Or, for email, use beazleyp@mqg-smtp3.usmc.mil!

This and future versions will be available for download from Aminet
and also from other SN PFile @{"Support Sites" link "SUPPORT"}.  To get a list
of all currently available and up-to-date SN PFiles, see the included
SN_Files.txt and SN_FilesInfo.txt or request info via email.

Suggestions are welcome!  Bug reports are mandatory!  :)

Beta-testers are needed for this and other SN PFiles.  Please send me
netmail if interested.

