@node "INFO" "SN Bulletins v2.1 - Information"
@toc "MAIN"
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
  SN Bulletins v2.1 - Information
└─────────────────────────────────┘

Welcome to my version of a Bulletins program.  It's formatted for two
columns and looks pretty nice.  There's not a whole lot to this, so let's
get to the point...

Features:
  - Indicates which bulletins have been updated since last call.

NOTE:  This is a compiled ARexx script.  However, it does not require any
       additional libraries or RPStart to function (unless otherwise
       noted in these docs).

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
